## 14. Personal Notes

This session demonstrated the power of **slow, methodical learning**:

1. Understand the concept (what is a question schema?)
2. Build it piece by piece (dataclasses, then generator, then main)
3. Test each piece (run after each chunk)
4. Verify the output (check question_bank.json)
5. Document everything (README, progress report)

This is how **professional AI systems are built** — not hacked together, but designed, implemented, tested, and documented.

The procurement tool is now at **33% complete**. The foundation is solid. Phases 3-6 will build on this.

